data.description:
Charming one-level with an open floor plan. Two main floor bedrooms and two main floor baths. Lower
level owner's suite with full bath, separate shower, make-up counter and walk-in closet.. Radon system installed in 2014. Drain-tiled lower level. Partially fenced backyard with gazebo and fire pit. 2-car insulated attached garage with garage door opener. Great SW location!
